541
00:42:00,920 --> 00:42:01,760
Sim.

542
00:42:03,280 --> 00:42:04,280
Amanhã?

543
00:42:04,400 --> 00:42:05,560
Sim, Rasmus.

544
00:42:22,480 --> 00:42:23,800
